data.description:
This stunning townhome-style condo, located at 11250 Florence St Unit 25C, offers two bedrooms and four bathrooms spread over 1,588 square feet. The home is spacious and only two years old, making it perfect for those seeking modern and comfortable living.

The home features balconies off of the living room and primary bedroom, providing a beautiful view of the surrounding area. The open floor plan makes it easy to entertain guests or spend quality time with family.

The two-car attached garage provides ample parking and additional storage space. The trendy and light cabinets and stainless steel appliances in the kitchen are sure to impress, making cooking a joy. 

Located in a desirable neighborhood, this home is just a short drive from all the amenities that the area has to offer, including top-rated schools, parks, and restaurants. Close to shopping, just off of 112th Ave and HWY 85. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a beautiful home in a great location! The price includes the 3 month old Samsung washer and dryer.
